#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/TimeConfigPanel.cpp:65
#: src/Dialogs/Device/Vega/LoggerParameters.hpp:12
#, no-c-format
msgid "UTC offset"
msgstr "UTC +/-"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/TimeConfigPanel.cpp:66
msgid ""
"The UTC offset field allows the UTC local time offset to be specified. The "
"local time is displayed below in order to make it easier to verify the "
"correct offset has been entered."
msgstr ""
"UTC odstupanje omogućuje specifikaciju vremenske razlike u UTC lokalnom "
"vremenu. Lokalne vrijeme se prikazuje iza svakog odstupanja, kako bi se "
"lakše verificiralo da je odstupanje postavljeno."

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/TimeConfigPanel.cpp:78
msgid "Use GPS time"
msgstr "Koristi GPS vrijeme"

#: src/Dialogs/Settings/Panels/TimeConfigPanel.cpp:79
msgid ""
"If enabled sets the clock of the computer to the GPS time once a fix is set."
" This is only necessary if your computer does not have a real-time clock "
"with battery backup or your computer frequently runs out of battery power or"
" otherwise loses time."
msgstr ""
"Ako je omogućeno, computer se setuje na GPS vremensku vrijednost kada je fix"
" postavljen. Ova funkcija je potrebna samo ako vaš computer nema real-time "
"vremenski određeni ili vaš computer neće biti u stanju da bude prikazan u "
"vrijeme kada je baterija izgubila snagu."

